    "biography": "<p>A multi-headed aquatic wyrm (Pleuracanthus polycaput) that develops a taste for flesh and savages anyone near its waters.</p><p><strong>Powers:</strong> None</p><p><em>Attacks: 10M, Reach +2 (multiple heads). Habitat: Deep lakes, deep river estuaries (rare). Range: Greece. Attacks within a 4 m radius (neck length) with 1D6 randomly-chosen heads per Complex Action; destroying one head doesn't stop the others. No more than 2 bites on a single man-sized target per melee Action. Swimming Quickness multiplier 7. Book Body 12/2, Intelligence 1/3. PAE p.61.</em></p>",
